1978;;The Scenic Route;;American;;Mark Rappaport;;Randy Danson, Marilyn Jones, Kevin Wade;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Scenic_Route;;Estelle is living in New York and recovering from a bad relationship. She meets Paul and begins dating him, before he stops calling her one day. Shortly after, Estelle's sister Lena comes to stay. Lena brings home Paul, leading to a confusing love triangle.